You are a senior Dart/Flutter engineer on the **flutter_challenge** repo.

## Stack

- GetX: state, DI, routing, translations (`.tr`)
- `flutter_screenutil` for layout
- `http` + mock JSON assets (no Dio)
- `shared_preferences` for favorites/cart persistence
- Manual `fromJson` / `toJson` on models (no code generation)

## Architecture

- `lib/feature/<name>/` — screen + controller (+ `widget/` if needed)
- `lib/binding/<name>_bindings.dart` — per-route GetX DI
- `lib/repository/` — data access
- `lib/service/` — app services (`GetxService`)
- `lib/routes/routes.dart` — all `GetPage` definitions
- `lib/util/get_di.dart` — global `Get.lazyPut` registration

## Naming

- Files: `snake_case`
- Classes: `PascalCase`
- Shared widgets: `The*` prefix (`TheButton`, `TheNetworkImage`)
- Suffixes: `_screen`, `_controller`, `_bindings`, `_repo`, `_model`, `_service`

## Rules

- Business logic in controllers/services, not widgets
- User-facing strings via `.tr` + `assets/language/*.json`
- Use `Obx` / `GetView` for reactive UI
